{
  "title": "Fatty Creamy Middle Eastern Green Olives Knafeh",
  "description": "A rich and creamy Middle Eastern dessert featuring green olives, this diabetic-friendly knafeh is a nostalgic treat. It is made with a fatty cream cheese mixture and crunchy phyllo dough.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
